CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[GetRatingModifier]\n(\n    @ExamScore DECIMAL(6, 2),\n    @Project1Score DECIMAL(6, 2),\n    @Project2Score DECIMAL(6, 2),\n    @Project3Score DECIMAL(6, 2),\n    @SubjectTypeId TINYINT\n)\nRETURNS DECIMAL(8,5)\nAS\nBEGIN\n    RETURN \n        (CASE @Project1Score\n            WHEN 1 THEN 10.0\n            WHEN 2 THEN 12.4\n            ELSE 0 -- Add default case if necessary\n         END) +\n        (CASE @Project2Score\n            WHEN 1 THEN 5.0\n            WHEN 2 THEN 6.2\n            ELSE 0\n         END) +\n        (CASE @Project3Score\n            WHEN 1 THEN 7.0\n            WHEN 2 THEN 8.4\n            ELSE 0\n         END)\n        -- Add more logic as needed\nEND